OL,5, The growing trend of children as young 
OL,6, as eight using skincare products could 
OL,7, leave them with irreversible skin      
OL,8, problems, the British Association for  
OL,9, Dermatologists has warned.             
OL,11,FSome children are asking their parents 
OL,12,Ffor luxury items after seeing them used
OL,13,Fby their favourite influencers on      
OL,14,Fplatforms such as YouTube and TikTok.  
OL,16,FBut many of these contain potentially  
OL,17,Fharmful active ingredients intended for
OL,18,Fadults only, such as exfoliating acids.
OL,20,FThey can provoke allergies or eczema.  
